#: WP-Res.php
msgid "This tool scans and removes hash placeholders (e.g., {ccea3ec6...}) that may remain after improper backups or migrations. It safely handles serialized data and supports batch processing, dry run, and transactions. Smart mode automatically restores content wrapped by paired hashes (e.g., {hash}%{hash} → %)."
msgstr "此工具扫描并移除不正确的备份或迁移后可能残留的哈希占位符（例如 {ccea3ec6...}）。它安全地处理序列化数据，支持批量处理、模拟运行和事务。智能模式自动还原被成对哈希包裹的内容（例如 {hash}%{hash} → %）。"

